A [[exchange|currency_exchange]] allowing trade between bitcoins and CAD (Canadian Dollar).

##Deposits

* Cash deposit at Royal Bank or Bank of Montreal (same business day)
* Wire transfer

##Withdrawals

* Canada Xpress Post Bank Draft (send by mail)
* Payza (formerly AlertPay) (withdrawn as CAD)
* Direct Deposit

##History
The exchange was opened on July 2, 2011 after weeks of Beta mode (4.1).  The exchange discontinued support for adding and withdrawing funds using Interac e-Transfers (EMTs) in August, 2011.

